#: ../../source/index.rst:7
msgid "Welcome to the Bone Physics documentation!"
msgstr "欢迎使用 Bone Physics 文档"

#: ../../source/index.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Bone Physics** is a `Blender` add-on that provides rigid-body-based "
"bone physics for dynamic elements such as hair, ribbons, and tails in "
"stylized character animation."
msgstr "**Bone Physics** 是一款 `Blender` 插件，用于在风格化角色动画中为头发、飘带、尾巴等动态元素创建基于刚体的骨骼物理模拟。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"This add-on is developed on top of |blender_mmd_tools|. Its goal is to "
"port the MMD physics system to `Blender` and use it as a standalone "
"module, making it compatible with `Blender`'s built-in **Rigify** "
"armature and other common rigging systems."
msgstr ""
"本插件基于 |blender_mmd_tools| 开发，目的是将 **MMD** 的物理系统移植到 Blender "
"中，并作为一个独立模块使用，从而兼容 `Blender` 内置的 **Rigify** 骨架以及其他常见绑定系统。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:16
msgid ""
"This add-on is open-source on |github| and distributed under the GPL-3.0 "
"license."
msgstr "本插件已在 |github| 上开源，并按照 GPL-3.0 许可证发布。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"If you would like to support its development, you may also purchase it on"
" |superhivemarket|, |gumroad|, and |bilibili_shop|."
msgstr "如果你愿意支持本插件的开发，也可以在 |superhivemarket|、|gumroad| 或 |bilibili_shop| 购买此插件。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:21
msgid ""
"Since this add-on is based on |blender_mmd_tools|, you can refer to the "
"physics setups used in many existing **MMD** models when configuring your"
" own characters."
msgstr "由于本插件基于 |blender_mmd_tools| 开发，在设置物理参数时，你可以参考许多现有 **MMD** 模型中的物理配置。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:24
msgid ""
"Video tutorials and complete workflow demonstrations are available on "
"|youtube_link| and |bilibili_link|."
msgstr "视频教程以及完整的工作流程演示可以在 |youtube_link| 和 |bilibili_link| 上查看。"

